, which you can see ironically with that interlanguagelink there the remnants of. That is what my original draft was about on enwiki (which you can see here ). I think most links are supposed to go there and not to the {{nihongo|{{ill|Yokoana-shiki sekishitsu|ja|横穴式石室|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokoana-shiki sekishitsu|13=User:Immanuelle/Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|qq=}}|横穴式石室|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|yokoana-shiki sekishitsu|qq=}} page. But I am not 100% sure.[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 04:40, 30 March 2025 (UTC)|qq=}}
|横穴式石室|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|1=Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|2=ja|3=横穴式石室|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|4=zh|5=橫穴式石室|6=ko|7=굴식 돌방무덤|yokoana-shiki sekishitsu|qq=}}. I find it rather absurd that I did that as it is relatively blatantly wrong, but I did not properly check. I am making a disambiguation page at  [[Corridor-type kofun]] that should be imported into wikipedia too, and we should sort out this issue before publishing either article for fear of having [[User:Cewbot]] correct the template to the wrong thing. Maybe just a mass replace of that text to [[Corridor-type kofun]] linking to the disambiguation page so disambiguation page fixer people can determine which one it is going to.[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 04:27, 30 March 2025 (UTC)|qq=}}
'''Corridor-type kofun''' can refer to the following
* {{nihongo|{{ill|Corridor-Style Stone Chamber|ja|横穴式石室}}|横穴式石室|3=yokoana-shiki sekishitsu|4=|5=|6=|7=|qq=}} Artificial stone chambers in Kofun
* {{nihongo|{{ill|corridor-type kofun|ja|横穴墓|lt=corridor-type ''kofun''|1=Yokoanabo|lt=Yokoanabo|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/corridor-type kofun|13=User:Immanuelle/Yokoanabo|qq=}}|横穴墓|yokōbo|qq=}} Tombs dug into artificial caves. These are technically not Kofun but often related archaeological sites
